```

### 2. AAA 模式
```typescript
it('应该正确计算进度', () => {
  // Arrange - 准备
  const current = 5
  const total = 10

  // Act - 执行
  const result = calculateProgress(current, total)

  // Assert - 断言
  expect(result).toBe(50)
})
```

### 3. 避免测试依赖
```typescript
// ❌ 错误：测试间有依赖
let counter = 0
it('测试1', () => { counter++ })
it('测试2', () => { expect(counter).toBe(1) })

// ✅ 正确：测试独立
it('测试1', () => { const counter = 0; counter++ })
it('测试2', () => { const counter = 0; expect(counter).toBe(0) })
```

